      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that still has plenty of life and spirit, you\u2019ve gotta come check this one out. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
