    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band and a 7,900 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushed control arms, while the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal mechanical grip under load. Maintenance is up to date with a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service. This is a mechanically sound example ready for spirited driving or track-day duty.",
