      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the hood\u2014honest evidence of its time on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, powerful engine that has never missed a beat. It is a dependable, stylish choice for someone who values a car that has been cared for with genuine pride of ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
