      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the M96/03 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a multilink rear suspension geometry that minimizes toe-steer under lateral load. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains dry. Braking is handled by Brembo-sourced four-piston monobloc calipers over vented rotors, showing minimal swept-area grooving. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-rash on the frontal fascia consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical integrity and throttle response are exceptionally sharp.",
